### APPOINTMENTS - GET ALL
GET http://localhost:8080//api/v1/appointments
Accept: application/json

### APPOINTMENTS - GET ONE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/1
Accept: application/json

### APPOINTMENTS - CREATE NEW ONE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient": {
    "name": "Chricro",
    "surname": "Crochri",
    "email": "chrui.chroi@gmail.com",
    "telephoneNumber": "31231231231"
  },
  "appointmentDate": "2026-03-10T13:00:00",
  "medicalExaminationType": "RADIOGRAPHY"
}

### MEDICAL EXAMINATION TYPE - GET ALL
GET http://localhost:8080//api/v1/medical-examination-types
Accept: application/json

### MEDICAL EXAMINATION TYPE - CREATE NEW ONE
POST http://localhost:8080//api/v1/medical-examination-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "RADIOGRAPHY",
    "description": "Reparto di radiografia"
}

### REPORT - CREATE NEW ONE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports?appointmentId=2
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MioBoundary

--MioBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
--MioBoundary--

### REPORT - GET ALL BY APPOINTMENT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports?appointmentId=1
Accept: application/json

### REPORT - GENERATE NEW TOKEN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/5/generate-token
Accept: application/json

### PUBLIC REPORT - GET ALL BY APPOINTMENT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/public/reports
Accept: application/json

### PUBLIC REPORT - GET ALL BY APPOINTMENT
